  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d96\u0dc2\u0db0 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc2\u0dca\u0db4\u0dcf\u0daf\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0d82\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d96\u0dc2\u0db0 \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c 3\u0da7 \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "High demand for the 3 types of medicines of the State Pharmaceutical Manufacturing Corporation",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A high official of the corporation said that there is a high demand for the three types of medicines that the State Pharmaceutical Manufacturing Corporation recently introduced in the local market namely levathirocin 50, omeparasol 20 and mefenamic acid 500.",
        "The officer who said that orders have been received covering the entire country for the three medicines, also stated that he is currently working to complete those orders in the best possible way.",
        "The official further said that at a time when the country is in a problematic situation with dollars, there is such a demand for a local product."
      ],
